# 5. ğŸ§± Medium-Term Roadmap (Beta â†’ Full Product)

### 5.1 Reliability Dashboard
- Highlight low-reliability statements
- Inline highlighting in draft text
- Heatmap mode (color-coded reliability)
- Suggested fixes (â€œRewrite this section?â€)

### 5.2 Output Comparison Tools
- Compare two versions:
  - Diff view
  - Highlighted additions & removals
  - Score changes (clarity, tone, structure)

### 5.3 Multi-Output Bundles
- Generate several deliverables at once:
  - Press release
  - Portfolio commentary
  - Investor email
- Cross-coherence enforcement

### 5.4 Templated Word/PPT Output
- Word template engine (docx)
- PPT slides with:
  - Summary bullets
  - Charts (later)
- User-defined templates per client/team

### 5.5 Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
- View-only roles
- Editor roles
- Admin roles
- Audit logs (enterprise)

