# 6. ğŸ§  Long-Term (Enterprise / v3+)

### 6.1 Internal Knowledge Base Integration
- Let users upload approved content to a private datastore
- ChromaDB / Pinecone / pgvector / Azure Search
- Retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) mode
- â€œApprove this version for trainingâ€ workflow
- Optional: auto-tagging & metadata extraction

### 6.2 Data Governance & Compliance
- Automatic detection of sensitive content
- Blocked phrases awareness
- Client-specific redaction rules
- Multi-region data residency (EU/US/APAC)

### 6.3 Enterprise Integrations
- SSO (Okta / Azure AD / Google)
- Slack/Teams notifications (â€œYour draft is readyâ€)
- Export to internal content systems
- Integration with deal workflow tools (DealCloud, Salesforce, etc.)

